shortdesc.ph: Reports the result of uploading the SDK log files.

section.p: After is called, the SDK triggers the callback to report the result of uploading the SDK log files. If the upload fails, refer to the reason parameter to troubleshoot.

plentry.pd: The request ID. The request ID is the same as the requestId returned in . You can associate specific uploads with callbacks through the requestId.

pd.p:
Whether the log file is uploaded successfully:
: Successfully upload the log files.
: Fails to upload the log files. For details, see the reason parameter.

plentry.pd: The reason for the upload failure. See .
